@baseUrl = http://localhost:5100
@nfcToken = change-me

### NFC card clocks with default toggle action
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/nfc/clock
Content-Type: application/json
X-Nfc-Reader-Token: {{nfcToken}}

{
  "cardId": "04 AA BB CC DD 11 80",
  "terminalId": "stempeluhr-pi-01",
  "action": "toggle"
}

### Latest NFC event for kiosk display
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/nfc/events/latest?terminalId=stempeluhr-pi-01
